cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.RO

This paper deals with visual recognition and reasoning tasks, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of program synthesis and machine learning algorithms also suggests that it could be relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of spatial relations and image parsing could also make it relevant to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
